# accessLevel

**Instance Property**

The subscriber’s level of access to your catalog of content.

## Declaration

```swift
var accessLevel: VSSubscriptionAccessLevel { get set }
```

## Discussion

An error occurs if you try to set this property to [doc://com.apple.videosubscriberaccount/documentation/VideoSubscriberAccount/VSSubscriptionAccessLevel/unknown].

## Setting Subscription Details

- **VSSubscriptionAccessLevel**: Constants representing a subscriber’s level of access to your content.
- **billingIdentifier**: The subscriber’s billing group.
- **expirationDate**: The date when the user’s subscription expires.
- **tierIdentifiers**: A list of content from your catalog that the subscriber can access.
